title: Looking for people to play with (HAVE TO HAVE SKYPE) OCEANIA ONLY
body: Since I never have people to play with and im always bored, im looking for people to play with comment down below your skype and LoL name and ill add you. (Mines iNachozHD) OCEANIA ONLY
